    {"id": "musk", "type": "text", "text": "## ELON MUSK\nLargest 2024 Trump donor\n\n- X acquisition Oct 2022\n- $280M+ Trump donations\n- DOGE leader (until mid-2025)\n- xAI, Tesla, SpaceX", "x": 200, "y": -200, "width": 320, "height": 200},

    {"id": "sacks", "type": "text", "text": "## DAVID SACKS\nAI/Crypto Czar\n\n- PayPal Mafia\n- All-In Podcast co-host\n- Trump 2.0 appointment\n- Craft Ventures", "x": -700, "y": 100, "width": 320, "height": 180},

