    {"id": "yarvin", "type": "text", "text": "## CURTIS YARVIN\nIntellectual godfather\n\n- Neoreactionary movement\n- 'Cathedral' critique\n- 'RAGE: Retire All Govt Employees'\n- Cited by Vance\n- Thiel-backed", "x": -300, "y": 400, "width": 320, "height": 220},

