    {"id": "palantir", "type": "text", "text": "## PALANTIR\nGovernment surveillance\n\n- Thiel co-founded\n- ICE, NSA, CIA, DoD client\n- Primary DOGE contractor 2025+\n- CA-adjacent (Chmieliauskas)", "x": 1100, "y": -10, "width": 280, "height": 220},

